[IMG]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TeamExodus/community_support/EXODUS-5.1/Exodus-About.png[/IMG]
EXODUS is an open-source project coded by professional level developers, focusing on improved versions of common features and improvements found in the open-source community while bringing new improvements and original coding with the highest standards.

[IMG]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TeamExodus/community_support/EXODUS-5.1/Exodus-Installation.png[/IMG]
[LIST]
[*]Be rooted w/ a custom recovery
[*]Download EXODUS Rom & Gapps for your device and move them to your phone
[*]Reboot to Recovery
[*]Wipe (Full wipe if coming from another Rom)**
[*]Flash the Rom
[*]Flash the Gapps**
[*]Reboot to System
[*]Setup and Reboot System
[/LIST]
These directions are not necessary after the first install if you use the Exodus Updater, included in the ROM.  It can notify you of updates, download, and install them for you automatically.

**This is automated if coming from a previous Exodus build (Dirty Flashing).

